echnology/singapore-vietnam-firms-talks-new-undersea-cables-sources-say-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>黄金将每周上涨，关注美联储政策决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-set-weekly-gain-with-focus-feds-policy-decision-2024-12-13/</link><description>受中国恢复黄金购买的报道以及美联储在 12 月 17 日至 18 日会议上降息的预期的推动，金价周五小幅走高，预计周度上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 03:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-set-weekly-gain-with-focus-feds-policy-decision-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市下跌，长期国债将迎来一年来最糟糕的一周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-13/</link><description>亚洲股市周五下跌，原因是美元走强导致风险情绪脆弱，而随着美国 2025 年大幅降息的预期消退，长期国债收益率有望创下今年最大单周涨幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥参议院批准应用程序驱动程序的工作福利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexican-senate-approves-work-benefits-app-drivers-2024-12-13/</link><description>墨西哥参议院周四批准了一项改革，以改善滴滴、Rappi 和 Uber 等网约车和送货服务司机的工作条件，确保他们获得社会保障和圣诞奖金等福利。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexican-senate-approves-work-benefits-app-drivers-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>油价企稳，录得三年来首周上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-lower-2025-supply-surplus-forecast-set-notch-weekly-gain-2024-12-13/</link><description>由于对伊朗和俄罗斯的额外制裁加剧了供应忧虑，而盈余前景打压市场，油价周五企稳，将迎来自 11 月底以来的首次周度上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-lower-2025-supply-surplus-forecast-set-notch-weekly-gain-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国打破对可能举行演习的沉默，称对台独活动不会手软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/breaking-silence-possible-drills-china-says-will-not-be-soft-taiwan-independence-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国国防部周五打破了对台湾周边几天军事活动的沉默，称是否举行演习由中国决定，军队在打击分裂势力的过程中“不会缺席”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:43:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/breaking-silence-possible-drills-china-says-will-not-be-soft-taiwan-independence-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>前中国队主教练李铁因受贿罪被判有期徒刑20年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-sentences-former-national-soccer-coach-20-years-prison-bribery-state-media-2024-12-13/</link><description>周五，中国在打击足球腐败方面取得了一个引人注目的成果，前埃弗顿中场球员、国家队主教练李铁因行贿和受贿被判处 20 年有期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-sentences-former-national-soccer-coach-20-years-prison-bribery-state-media-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示将“根据斗争形势”决定在台湾周边举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-will-decide-hold-military-exercises-around-taiwan-according-situation-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国周五表示，将“根据自身需要和斗争形势”决定是否举行军事演习，以应对台湾总统赖清德最近访美。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-will-decide-hold-military-exercises-around-taiwan-according-situation-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾在美国支持下在南海“挑衅”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-has-provoked-trouble-south-china-sea-with-us-backing-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国周五指责菲律宾在美国的支持下在南海“挑衅”，一周前北京和马尼拉就争议海域发生的新对抗相互指责。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-has-provoked-trouble-south-china-sea-with-us-backing-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>全球电动汽车销量连续第三次创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-hit-third-consecutive-record-high-2024-12-13/</link><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 周五公布的数据显示，11 月份全球纯电动和插电式混合动力汽车销量连续第七个月增长，同比增长 32%，连续第三次创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 00:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-hit-third-consecutive-record-high-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国考虑人民币贬值，特朗普贸易顾问警告不要操纵汇率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trump-trade-adviser-warns-against-currency-manipulation-china-mulls-weaker-yuan-2024-12-12/</link><description>候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的高级贸易顾问周四告诉路透社，新政府不会“热衷于”中国操纵人民币的任何企图，回应路透社有关中国当局正在考虑允许人民币下一步贬值的报道。年。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trump-trade-adviser-warns-against-currency-manipulation-china-mulls-weaker-yuan-2024-12-12/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国深化经济刺激，全球信号喜忧参半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 21:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>